name: The EpilepsiaAI Project #0016
description:
Last night I had a seizure, and my computer made some art in response.

-----------

An AI-generated collection about my battle with epilepsy and seizures using text-to-image AI models.

Seed image from a photo taken of me prior to an inpatient Video-EEG monitoring session. 

For more information on the project see failoften.net or @EpilepsiaAI on Twitter.

Format: MP4
Time: 8 seconds
